.TH "clk_get_scaled_duty_cycle" 9 "clk_get_scaled_duty_cycle" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
clk_get_scaled_duty_cycle \- return the duty cycle ratio of a clock signal
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" clk_get_scaled_duty_cycle
.BI "(struct clk *clk "  ","
.BI "unsigned int scale "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "clk" 12
clock signal source
.IP "scale" 12
scaling factor to be applied to represent the ratio as an integer
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns the duty cycle ratio of a clock node multiplied by the provided
scaling factor, or negative errno on error.
